Class ContractMemory

java.lang.Object
  pt.unl.fct.di.dbc4j.ContractMemory

public class ContractMemory
extends java.lang.Object

Class for memorizing the old state of an object or member. This class is a stub, requiring ContractMemoryAspect advice to run.

Author:
